{
  "id": "adv_card_mna_02_03",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 3話 あの頃から変わらない気持ち",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-11.m4a",
      "text": "あーあ、楽しい時間はいつもあっという間だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh‚ fun times always go by so quickly‚ don't they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-01.m4a",
      "text": "今日で休暇はおしまいか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our vacation ends today…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-04.m4a",
      "text": "名残惜しいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's too bad…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-night",
      "startTime": 9.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-01.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、{user}くん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_enter-01.m4a",
      "text": "もうちょっとだけ、遊んで帰らない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can't we play a little more before heading back?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……ダメだ。明日からまた忙しくなるんだから\n家でゆっくり休んでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ we can't. It's going to get busy again tomorrow.\nRest and relax at home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-night",
      "startTime": 19.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-08.m4a",
      "text": "あー！　マネージャーモードになってる！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh! You're in manager mode now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-06.m4a",
      "text": "今日一日は、仕事抜きって言ったのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said today would be work-free!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "もう遊園地は出たんだから\n元に戻ってもいいだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're already out of the amusement park‚\nSo it's okay to go back to normal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-night",
      "startTime": 29.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-04.m4a",
      "text": "相変わらずお堅いね、{user}くんは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're still so serious‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-02.m4a",
      "text": "ワーカホリックってやつじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you a workaholic?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-04.m4a",
      "text": "今からこんなんじゃ、数年後が心配だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm worried about you in a few years from now at this rate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-night",
      "startTime": 38.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈にだけは言われたくないよ\n大体、麻奈の担当だと、自然に仕事が増えるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to hear that from you‚ Mana.\nBesides‚ when I'm in charge of you‚ work naturally increases.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-03.m4a",
      "text": "確かにそうだね！　あはは！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true! Ahaha!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（……それに、麻奈と一緒の仕事は楽しいし、な）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Besides‚ working with Mana is enjoyable‚ isn't it?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-night",
      "startTime": 56.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-05.m4a",
      "text": "…………ねぇ、{user}くん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_emb-02.m4a",
      "text": "もし私がアイドル辞めちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I quit being an idol",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ただの普通の女の子に戻るって言ったら、どうする？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And said I wanted to be just a normal girl again‚ what would you do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "え……？　麻奈、何を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…? Mana‚ what are you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-night",
      "startTime": 69.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-01.m4a",
      "text": "私も{user}くんも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both {user} and I",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "アイドルとマネージャーの関係じゃなくなるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wouldn't be idol and manager anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-06.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたら、{user}くんはどうする？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what would you do‚ {user}?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうしたい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you want?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-night",
      "startTime": 80.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-05.m4a",
      "text": "私達どんな関係になるんだろうね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder what kind of relationship we would have?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-night",
      "startTime": 86.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "…………俺は\n俺は、長瀬麻奈の歌が好きだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I\nI‚ I love Mana Nagase's singing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……うん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-night",
      "startTime": 94.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "だからお前に誘われた時、マネージャーになったんだ\nあの頃から、その気持ちは変わらない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why I became your manager when you invited me.\nSince then‚ my mindset haven't changed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈が歌うのをやめるなんて、考えられないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't imagine you stopping singing‚ Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-01.m4a",
      "text": "……そっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistation-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistation-00-night",
      "startTime": 110
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ありがとう、嬉しいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ I'm happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
